00:38:46.520 --> 00:38:48.360
How are you controlling access

00:38:48.360 --> 00:38:49.560
to open source libraries

00:38:49.560 --> 00:38:51.080
that aren't developed in-house

00:38:51.879 --> 00:38:55.719
so that you can satisfy

00:38:55.719 --> 00:38:57.399
