00:38:57.399 --> 00:38:59.639
and, you know, make sure

00:38:59.639 --> 00:39:01.159
you're not accidentally

00:39:01.159 --> 00:39:02.280
introducing issues

00:39:02.280 --> 00:39:03.560
with breaking changes?

00:39:05.159 --> 00:39:08.199
Yeah, we do have platform teams

00:39:08.199 --> 00:39:10.360
that do host a lot of these libraries.

00:39:11.080 --> 00:39:14.600
Honestly, some of it's more of a pain

00:39:14.600 --> 00:39:15.639
