00:39:15.639 --> 00:39:16.919
than I'd say it is for

00:39:18.360 --> 00:39:19.239
the governance side.

00:39:19.239 --> 00:39:21.080
We're pretty slow to sometimes

00:39:21.080 --> 00:39:22.679
