00:39:22.679 --> 00:39:24.919
some of the libraries and packages

00:39:24.919 --> 00:39:26.679
and versions and things.

00:39:28.280 --> 00:39:29.320
But I'd say, you know,

00:39:29.320 --> 00:39:30.840
we do try to govern those.

00:39:30.840 --> 00:39:33.080
We try to have a, you know, V plus one

00:39:33.080 --> 00:39:35.000
so that we're managing, you know,

00:39:35.000 --> 00:39:37.159
not only the existing version

00:39:37.159 --> 00:39:39.080
of the library, but the next one

00:39:39.080 --> 00:39:41.320
and maintaining the one behind it as well.

00:39:41.879 --> 00:39:42.840
So that we do have the right

00:39:42.840 --> 00:39:43.959
change management in there.

00:39:44.679 --> 00:39:45.719
But the platform team

00:39:45.719 --> 00:39:46.840
