00:45:35.000 --> 00:45:35.639
I'd say we,

00:45:36.280 --> 00:45:37.719
especially with like tech blogs

00:45:37.719 --> 00:45:38.679
and the open source stuff

00:45:38.679 --> 00:45:39.479
