00:46:57.239 --> 00:46:58.439
It's about Abraham Lincoln.

00:47:00.360 --> 00:47:02.840
It's pretty in depth.

00:47:02.840 --> 00:47:03.800
It's a deep read,

00:47:03.800 --> 00:47:05.800
but it is fantastic

00:47:05.800 --> 00:47:07.080
