00:47:16.120 --> 00:47:18.199
And I just think it was,

00:47:18.199 --> 00:47:19.560
it's an amazing read.

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:23.080
And I think you just learn a lot

00:47:23.080 --> 00:47:25.239
